<br />\n<br />\n點解好似比我想像中平...<br />\n定係當年價"},{"pid":"1c19bc2e70c3dd1888a5c1bd630e3efefbdde130","tid":645224,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:44:04.000Z","msg":"點跳呀佢"},{"pid":"96ee92b4b1be8cfe99af2ff9079f14ad170bec73","tid":645224,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:45:09.000Z","msg":"米卡羅指金正恩曾向自己披露真正身份<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真正朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f44a4da51c5f0dbe3262c1e25e5155312446e00","tid":645224,"uid":109573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c19bc2e70c3dd1888a5c1bd630e3efefbdde130","tid":645224,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:44:04.000Z","msg":"點跳呀佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:45:17.000Z","msg":"巴打 rip"},{"pid":"9214f616a764a224edee635c07d6942c59d35254","tid":645224,"uid":51152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fcf3947ed21eee944eba11993c2a43cfcb235d87","tid":645224,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:43:15.000Z","msg":"刺殺金正恩劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:45:30.000Z","msg":"有打籃波既描寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n假隨和真兇狠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0cb03e54fff18d675c6c0ab7ec1feeffc35214","tid":645224,"uid":96,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:46:35.000Z","msg":"米卡羅指金正恩曾向自己披露真正身份，但由於金正恩並非住在大使館，而是住在學校附近一處高檔住宅區，他起初以為對方「吹水」。<br />\n<br />\n佢知道係真個時有冇嚇撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed439e1d5130a5c1a04f24e80328db64a25d13e8","tid":645224,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T04:15:44.000Z","msg":"她說金正恩從不惹事，但缺乏容忍度，有時會發脾氣，當被責罵時不會駁嘴，但會用不吃東西等方式來表達不滿